--- license: mit --- # Introduction QTC4SO(Qusetion Title Completion for Stack Overflow) is a pre-trained model based on T5. We fine-tuned it on our downstream task. It is used for question title completion on StackOverflow # More details You can find our code and dataset on our [GitHub project](https://github.com/shaoyuyoung/QTC4SO)
For more details, please refer to [our paper](https://smartse.github.io/paper/icpc2023.pdf)
